name: Red India on Dupioni Silk Ring Sling
description:
A beautiful sling made with luxurious fabrics!  The red floral cotton print is imported straight from India, and is combined with gorgeous dupioni silk.  This is a Le Due (double fabric) sling featuring a plush shoulder pad for comfort and aluminum rings for strength.  It is a size smaller than my standard in length.  Would be best for 20lb and under. 
An awesome gift for the first-time mom with a fall baby!

name: Apple on Blue Ring Sling
description:
Bright and beautiful!  The bold and sharp colors on this sling will sure to get a few extra baby complements while out!  This is a Le Due (double fabric) sling featuring a short shoulder pad and pleats for comfort.  It is a bit longer than my standard size and has a pocket on the blue tail.  Both materials are 100% cotton.
Reversible!

name: Dots and Silver Ring Sling
description:
Any mom's outfit will be instantly updated with this custom sling, ultra modern ring sling!   This Le Due (double fabric) sling features fun colors, a plush shoulder pad, aluminum rings and a cotton/poly blend.  Great size for a taller mom, but will any parent and baby/toddler will love it.
Reversible!

name: Pink Paisley on Black Ring Sling
description:
Any mom's outfit will be instantly updated with this sleek black and pink ring sling!   This Le Due (double fabric) sling features a plush shoulder pad, pocket, aluminum rings and a cotton/poly blend.  Works well in spring and winter.
Reversible!

name: Fancy Green on Black Ring Sling
description:
One of my favorite color combinations!  A Le Due (double fabric) sling featuring a shoulder pad and pleats for comfort.  It is my standard size and has a pocket on the black tail.  Both materials are 100% cotton.
Reversible and Beautiful!
